snippet.title: Finding Frankie - Official Announcement Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Finding Frankie is a first-person parkour horror game developed by the Finding Frankie Team. Players will tackle obstacle courses by jumping, climbing, and swinging to evade a cast of horrifying characters. Finding Frankie is launching in 2024 for PC (Steam).
